       "abc.ABCMeta.register.__qualname__.__len__() == 16 — 'ABCMeta.register' has 16 characters: A-B-C-M-e-t-a-.-r-e-g-i-s-t-e-r; str.__len__() returns 16; new to abc_extra178"]

